component_text: most of people do not have a plan for make a limitation or schedule for watching television
In spite of enjoying watching television shows, it is really time consuming task
Emergence of new television channels or shows are not surprising
We kill time by tracking these channels so at the end of the day we understand it is late for doing any other activities
This is a problem that suffers all of us everyday
there is no time for call to our parents or friends
watching television programs makes us lazy
We usually spend our times in front of television for at least three ours a day when we come back home after eight-hour working in the office
we do not have time to spend for healthy activity such as going to a gym or doing other sports
This makes us a lazy person who prefers to do sedentary activities like watching television shows rather than be active and sociable
some television programs have a negative effect on viewers
Some thriller or action movies advertise negative activities such as doing criminal activity
These genre of programs has more negative effects on our teenagers
They usually try to mimic what they see on movies in their daily behaviors
killing our time, making us lazy, and advertising negative behaviors are just only few reasons to show how television is destructive
it is a global problem to solve this problem and it is need global contribution to find a solution
